.TH LOA-SHEET-STATS 1 "2026-03-23" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
sheet stats \- Show sheet-music-specific statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> sheet stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
Shows aggregate statistics for \fBSheetMusic\fR entries:
.br
- total sheet music count
.br
- top composers
.br
- top instrumentation
.br
- difficulty split
.br
- practice status split
